-- Metro Third-Quarter Net Beats Estimate as Revenue Rises; Raises Forecast
-- B y   H o l g e r   E l f e s
-- 2010-11-02T06:15:00Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-02/metro-third-quarter-net-beats-estimate-as-revenue-rises-raises-forecast.html
Metro AG  reported third-quarter net
income of 149 million euros, beating an analyst estimate of 114
million euros, as sales increased. The company, which reported
in a statement released to reporters today, raised its full-year
earnings before interest and taxes forecast.  To contact the reporter responsible for this story:
